## 8. Open Questions / To-Do

### High Priority
1. **Exact story scene count and order** - Story unfinished; keep logic scene-count-agnostic
2. **Hidden driver thresholds** - Exact cutoffs for endings 1/2/3 need tuning after first full playthrough
3. **Voluntary early merge** - Whether player can merge early after unlock, or only when sleep forces it
4. **Hex board items** - Final item set (target: 2-3 items)
5. **Gotchi sprite** - Canonical sprite choice for Gary needs commitment

### Stretch / Lower Priority
1. Multi-Gotchi social system
2. Environment integration (temperature, weather, time of day)
3. Growth system (life stages)
4. Inventory system
5. Skill learning system

